Posted By: Jay
DOLEYNIGLE was the way they spelled Dalrymple on this SGC10 Old Judge card. While spelling errors are not that unusual in the Old Judge set, none is close to being as pronounced as this one. This is your basic random letter accumulation. A very scarce and unusual card with corner wear and a name handstamp and writing on the back.----$1000. Please email me  for scans at oldjudge@gmail.com

Thanks!
